    "content": "<h3>About Us</h3>\n<p style=\"language: en-IN; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-font-family: Helvetica; mso-fareast-font-family: Helvetica; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; language: en-GB;\">This stylish 5 &ndash; floor hotel provides great town view and amazing scenery views, with sea and mountains surrounding the hotel. In the basement area is a luxury spa- and fitness centre so it&rsquo;s ideal to relax there after a hard day sightseeing. The hotel is located in Borgarnes, West Iceland.</span></p>\n<p style=\"language: en-IN; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-font-family: Helvetica; mso-fareast-font-family: Helvetica; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; language: en-GB;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"language: en-IN; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-font-family: Helvetica; mso-fareast-font-family: Helvetica; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; language: en-GB;\">Our restaurant serves everything from bistro to a la carte menu and our bar is well known for great selection of local beer.</span></p>\n<p style=\"language: en-IN; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-left: 0in; text-indent: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-font-family: Helvetica; mso-fareast-font-family: Helvetica; mso-bidi-font-family: Helvetica; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: mino